uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request

Class DataRequestResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.Request
      • uk.gov.gchq.palisade.service.request.DataRequestResponse

  • public class DataRequestResponse
extends Request
    This is the high level API object that is used to pass back to the client the information it requires to connect to the correct data service implementations and to decide how best to parallelise their job.

    It is also the object that the client then passes to the data service to access the data. When it is passed to the data service the resources field might have been changed to be a subset of the resources.
